sources.title: Rock Baby - Rock It
sources.description: Title: Rock Baby - Rock It Summary: Local Dallas teenagers resist attempts by shady underworld types to take over their beloved rock 'n' roll club. This rock 'n' roll-themed movie features top-notch rockabilly performances by... Directed by: Murray Douglas Sporup Actors: Johnny Carroll, Don Coats, Preacher Smith Production Company: Evelyn-Rock Release Date: 29 May 1957 (USA) Aspect Ratio: REMOVE_TAG Local Dallas teenagers resist attempts by shady underworld types to take over their beloved rock 'n' roll club. This rock 'n' roll-themed movie features top-notch rockabilly performances by Don Coates and The Bon-Aires, Preacher Smith and the Deacons, The Five Stars, The Belew Twins, Johnny Carroll and Roscoe Gordon.
